      "widgets_values": [
        "With this custom node, you can preview a 3 shot sequence quickly with Sora.\n\nThis is the simplified version \u2014 for each of the 3 shots, set a description prompt, camera motion, and shot type from the dropdowns.\n\nThe node builds a prompt that is sent to OpenAI ChatGPT to generate a rich, Sora-optimized video prompt. The ChatGPT output then feeds directly into OpenAI Sora - Video.\n\nThis node creates a pre-prompt for ChatGPT to create your sequence in Sora."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
